data.description:
Welcome to the Lake Pointe Community, where beauty meets convenience! This lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house is a dream come true for anyone looking for a comfortable and stylish place to call home. Located within walking distance of Tarver Elementary School, North Belton Middle School, and Lake Belton High School, this house is perfect for families with children. The community is equipped with a pool, park, and is ideal for morning, afternoon, or evening walks.
As you step inside, you'll be impressed by the laminate wood flooring in the living area, kitchen, eat-in dining area, and hallways. The living room features a beautiful fireplace, perfect for cozy nights in with family and friends. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, ample storage space, a pantry, and an eat-in kitchen with a stunning updated matte black chandelier. You can enjoy your morning coffee on the covered front porch or relax in the evenings or entertain friends and family on the back patio with the gorgeous firepit while enjoying the beautiful night air.
The primary bedroom is spacious and features a walk-in closet and a primary suite bathroom that includes a dual vanity, jacuzzi tub, and walk-in shower with plenty of storage space for toiletries and linens. The two additional rooms are also a great size and feature ceiling fan/lights, large closets, and carpet. The secondary bathroom features a single vanity and a shower/tub combo, great for family or guests.
In summary, this is an amazing home that you wouldn't want to miss! With the convenience of its location and the comfort of its amenities, this house is perfect for anyone looking for a beautiful and cozy place to call home.
